OL,3,CWhen is the next heatwave? Forecasts
OL,4,Cshow return of 35C temperatures
OL,6,FTemperatures have barely dropped a few
OL,7,Fdegrees after an intense nationwide
OL,8,Fheatwave but it looks like another one
OL,9,Fis on the horizon.
OL,11,FAs we approach July, forecasts suggest
OL,12,Fthe UK will be heating up again to the
OL,13,Fsweltering conditions we saw last week.
OL,15,FWhat's in store this week?
OL,17,FThere'll be a return to lower
OL,18,Ftemperatures as we start the week -
OL,19,Fmore in line with a typical UK summer
OL,20,Ffor most of us.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
