OL,3,CWhen is the next heatwave? Forecasts
OL,4,Cshow return of 35C temperatures
OL,6,FIn some places temperatures are a good
OL,7,F10C lower than last week - when many
OL,8,Fareas reached close to 35-38C, peaking
OL,9,Fat 37.7C in Lingwood, Norfolk.
OL,11,FThe heat and humid air of last week
OL,12,Ftook longer to clear in parts of the
OL,13,Fsouth-east, so for many of us it's
OL,14,Fonly now that our air is feeling much
OL,15,Ffresher.
OL,17,FTemperatures will be a more
OL,18,Fcomfortable 20-25C today as heat and
OL,19,Fhumid air gives way.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
