OL,3,CWhen is the next heatwave? Forecasts
OL,4,Cshow return of 35C temperatures
OL,6,FThat's because our weather is
OL,7,Freturning to its normal influences;
OL,8,Fthe Atlantic Ocean and winds coming
OL,9,Ffrom the west.
OL,11,FMore showers with longer bursts of
OL,12,Frain will move into the north and west
OL,13,Fon Tuesday - with some bringing a
OL,14,Fchance of thunder.
OL,16,FThese storms may also progress across
OL,17,Fthe south and east.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
