OL,3,CWhen is the next heatwave? Forecasts
OL,4,Cshow return of 35C temperatures
OL,6,FLater in the week, as high pressure re-
OL,7,Festablishes itself from the south,
OL,8,Ftemperatures will be set to rise again
OL,9,Fwith highs of 25-28C across parts of
OL,10,FEngland and Wales.
OL,12,FScotland and Northern Ireland will
OL,13,Fstay a cooler and fresher.
OL,15,FWhen will we see another heatwave?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
