OL,3,CWhen is the next heatwave? Forecasts
OL,4,Cshow return of 35C temperatures
OL,6,FSome areas of the south-east of
OL,7,FEngland will be close to heatwave
OL,8,Fcriteria into next weekend as
OL,9,Ftemperatures reach close to 30C on
OL,10,FSaturday and more so on Sunday with
OL,11,Fhighs of 30-32C.
OL,13,FThe high pressure will build across
OL,14,Fthe south-west and parts of southern
OL,15,FBritain - the dry sunny conditions
OL,16,Fwill encourage rising temperatures
OL,17,Fagain.
OL,19,FThis heat will also lift the humidity
OL,20,Flevels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
