OL,3,CWhen is the next heatwave? Forecasts
OL,4,Cshow return of 35C temperatures
OL,6,FGenerally it'll be a more manageable
OL,7,Fthan last week's conditions.
OL,9,FHow hot could it be?
OL,11,FAt this stage, some forecast scenarios
OL,12,Fshow temperatures climbing close to
OL,13,F35C or more again.
OL,15,FIt looks like the heat will peak
OL,16,Facross the South and South East of the
OL,17,FUK from the beginning to middle of
OL,18,Fnext week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
