OL,3,CWhen is the next heatwave? Forecasts
OL,4,Cshow return of 35C temperatures
OL,6,FIt's expected to be much hotter next
OL,7,Fweek for many of us, with heatwave
OL,8,Fconditions again in some places,
OL,9,Faccompanied by warm, stuffy nights `
OL,10,Fbut updates to this forecast are
OL,11,Fexpected throughout the week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
